To get to the nearest bank, you should head over to Bank of Tanzania, which is located at Mwalimu Nyerere Road. All banks and ATMs can be found here. If you are in need of any public services, you can head to the nearest police station. However, if you are in need of any, the nearest police station is located 1.0km away. You can visit the police station at Mwalimu Nyerere Road. You can also visit the nearest post office at Mwalimu Nyerere Road. For all major national holidays, please visit the official website of United Republic of Tanzania.

If you are hungry or craving for something, head over to the nearest restaurant, which is Mawenzi Restaurant that is located at Mwalimu Nyerere Road. Please check the various categories of this page for various types of food and restaurants. If you are looking for a place to buy gifts or souvenirs, head over to the nearest shop, which is Mawenzi Shop that is located at Mwalimu Nyerere Road. You will be able to find anything you are looking for, from souvenirs to gifts in this shop.
